  EncounterId: H1_GREETING
  Type: 0
  QuestionTextAR: "\u0627\u0644\u0633\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0639\u0644\u064A\u0643\u0645
    \u0643\u064A\u0641 \u062D\u0627\u0644\u0643\u061F"
  Choices:
  - TextAR: "\u0645\u0631\u062D\u0628\u0627"
    BatteryDelta: -0.15
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 0
    ScrapReward: 2
    IsCorrect: 0
    FeedbackText: Generic and too casual for Eid. The occasion calls for a full blessing.
  - TextAR: "\u0639\u064A\u062F \u0645\u0628\u0627\u0631\u0643 \u0643\u0644 \u0639\u0627\u0645
      \u0648\u0623\u0646\u062A\u0645 \u0628\u062E\u064A\u0631"
    BatteryDelta: 0.1
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 5
    ScrapReward: 5
    IsCorrect: 1
    FeedbackText: The complete Eid greeting. Returning a full blessing shows genuine
      cultural fluency.
  - TextAR: "\u0647\u0644\u0627"
    BatteryDelta: -0.25
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 0
    ScrapReward: 1
    IsCorrect: 0
    FeedbackText: "Informal slang. Using it with elders on Eid is considered disrespectful
      \u2014 \u0639\u064A\u0628."
